
uob_hep_pc065d

These file describes PCB fabrication and assembly details of a 
Fibre Interface Board (FIB) for the DUNE Timing System.


contact:	David.Cussans@bristol.ac.uk
		tel: 0117 95 46879
		     0117 33 17199
		fax: 0117 925 5624

Files produced by Cadence DE-HDL / Allegro 24.1

Artwork:
--------

Format: Gerber RS-274X , parameters described in art_param.txt. 
All layers viewed from top

Build:
------

Eight Layers as follows:

art_pc065d_L01P.ger
art_pc065d_L02P.ger
art_pc065d_L03P.ger
art_pc065d_L04P.ger
art_pc065d_L05P.ger
art_pc065d_L06P.ger
art_pc065d_L07P.ger
art_pc065d_L08P.ger

FR4 or similar laminate

35um copper on outers ( after plating )
18um copper on inners

Solder Masks
------------

art_pc065d_LSM1.ger
art_pc065d_LSM2.ger

Colour not critical, suggest green. Photo-imagable.

Solderpaste mask
-----------------

art_pc065d_SMD1.ger
art_pc065d_SMD2.ger

Silk screen
-----------

art_pc065d_POS1.ger
art_pc065d_POS2.ger

Colour not critical, suggest white.

Assembly Diagram
-----------------

art_pc065d_ASSEMBLY_TOP.ger
art_pc065d_ASSEMBLY_BOTTOM.ger


Board outline: (Gerber RS-274X)
-------------------------------

art_pc065d_OUTLINE.ger

For details of FMC standard board outline see ansi_vita_57.1_double_fmc_outline.pdf

Drill figure: ( illustration of hole sizes and position )
-------------

art_pc065d_DRILL_FIGURE.ger

Drill information ( Excellon format, described in nc_param.txt )
-----------------
Plated and unplated holes in same file.

pc065d_fibv2a_toplevel_29-1-8.drl

Bill of Materials
-----------------

pc065d_fibv2a_bom.xlsx


Component placement
-------------------

pc065d_fibv2a_placement_body_centre.txt

